            "id": 6432316,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 新思科技(SNPS-US)大漲5.07%，報479.99美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新思科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SNPS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SNPS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SNPS-US</a>)截至台北時間24日21:34股價上漲23.14美元，報479.99美元，漲幅5.07%，成交量104,284（股），盤中最高價479.99美元、最低價469.19美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.36%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.25%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.76%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+4.21%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>新思科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SNPS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SNPS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SNPS-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+3.56%</li> <li>近 1 月：+5.63%</li> <li>近 3 月：-8.88%</li> <li>近 6 月：+0.17%</li> <li>今年以來：-2.74%</li></ul></section></main>",
